            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/imgs/lungs.jpg" class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="Responsive image">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Without the organ donor there is no story, no hope, no transplant. But when there is an organ donor,
                    life springs from death, sorrow turns to hope and a terrible loss becomes a gift.</h5>
                <p>– United Network for Organ Sharing.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
